         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 9 of Lucius Septimius Severus Pius Pertinax and Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Pius Augusti and Publius Septimius Geta Caesar Augustus. Work done on the dikes for year 9, Payni from 26 till 30, at the canal of Hermoithes, on behalf of Tebtunis for five days, (2nd h.) by Didymas, slave of Hiera, five days. The 2nd penthemeros.</ab>
